<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script defer="" src="7deddbeceb51cfd3b4ee4302c7736711"></script>
    <title>Game of Life</title>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="main-container">
        <aside class="aside">
            <h1 class="title">Game of Life</h1>
            <button id="open-modal" class="aside__rules-btn">See rules</button>
            <div class="x-center">
                <input type="checkbox" id="autoplay" class="autoplay">
                <label for="autoplay" class="btn">Go!</label>
            </div>
        </aside>
        <table id="board" class="board"></table>
    </main>
    <div id="modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal__content">
            <span id="close-modal" class="modal__close">&times;</span>
            <ul>
                <li>Any dead cell with three live neighbors becomes a live cell.</li>
                <li>Any live cell with two or three live neighbors survives.</li>
                <li>All other live cells die in the next generation. Similarly, all other dead cells stay dead.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>    
</body>

</html>